snippet.title: Minecraft x Jurassic World Adventures
snippet.description: Jurassic World is roaring its way back into the Minecraft Marketplace! Step into a modern world with pixelated prehistoric predators, thriving in a variety of environments.  Play as your favorite characters from the franchise as you explore a massive world filled with living, breathing dinosaurs. Learn to fend off poachers, protect dinosaurs, collect, unlock, and escape apex predators.
